'''James Ohlen''' was a studio director from [[BioWare]]. For ''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]'', he is credited as the lead designer, one of seven members of the core design team, and one of four manual writers. For [[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords|the sequel]], he received special thanks. He was also a lead designer on ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''.

